| Phase | Time | Focus | Who |
|-------|------|-------|-----|
| **Phase 0** | 0:00–0:30 | Setup & Prerequisites | All |
| **Phase 1** | 0:30–2:00 | AWS Deploy + Backend Working | 🟣M1 + 🔵M3 |
