## 📞 Communication Plan

- **Group chat**: Share API URL, report bugs, coordinate merges
- **Every 1 hour**: Quick standup — "What did you finish? What are you stuck on?"
- **Before merge**: Alert the team, merge one at a time to avoid conflicts
- **Before demo**: Full team dry run — everyone watches, catches issues
